      {
        "inline": {
          "part_type": "Heading",
          "text": [
            "تَمَّ كِتَابُ الْأَطْعِمَةِ وَ يَتْلُوهُ كِتَابُ الْأَشْرِبَةِ إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ وَ الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ وَحْدَهُ وَ الصَّلَاةُ عَلَى مَنْ لَا نَبِيَّ بَعْدَهُ ."
          ],
          "translations": {
            "en.hubeali": [
              "The Book of Foodstuffs is completed and it would be followed by the Book of Drinks, Allah<sup>azwj</sup> Willing, and the Praise is for Allah<sup>azwj</sup>, One, and the Blessings be upon the one after whom<sup>saww</sup> there is no Prophet<sup>as</sup>."
            ]
          }
        },
        "part_type": "Heading"
      }
    ],
